title: Steal Like An Artist
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
On this week's episode of #TheFriendZone, we continue our discussion on Intellectual Property Laws, sharing a recent experience with theft, discussing our own biggest influences and whether or not stricter laws would interfere with the evolution of thought and the progression of art.
